description:
Band: Bodycall
Title: Somatic Turn
Year: 2003
Format: FLAC
Label: Halotan Records / halotan.net

Originally released in 2003 Somatic Turn is now an example of oldschool/classic EBM, Synthpop or Electro Industrial. 

Created with limited technical resources available at the time the release is raw and unpolished. 

The package contains original covers as well as modified re-relase booklet. Physical CD can be purchased at www.halotan.net 

If you are looking for more dark electronic, synthpop, goth, ebm music head to halotan.net and download for free!
